==================================
Saints Row IV is a 2013 open world action-adventure video game developed by Volition and published by Deep Silver. It was released in August 2013 for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360. It is the fourth installment in the Saints Row series, after the release of Saints Row: The Third in 2011. As in previous titles in the series, the player controls the leader of the Third Street Saints, a street gang, who has now become the president of the United States.
